Title: Defeat Krampus
Description:
This is a story-like challenge made for the contest.
Your goal is to defeat Krampus by getting into his castle and destroying his strongest minions.
Blue explanation marks are hints.
Collect 6 red & green cubes to unlock a secret.
You can also find secret shortcuts to make it easier for yourself.

Good luck!
